title: Hot Jamz!
content: Tough one, Tiff -- the closest I've been able to find is [Pneuma](http://web.archive.org/web/20050525002218/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/letraset/pneuma/pneuma/testdrive.html?s=HOT%2B103%2BJAMS&p=72), but it doesn't have the same rough energy as the sample.
author: cheshiredave
